Heritrix-as-a-WAR uses the containers&#39; authentication mechanism.  If you 
haven&#39;t already, set up an &#39;admin&#39; role with login/password for your 
container -- for tomcat, edit ${TOMCAT_HOME}/conf/tomcat-users.xml -- 
and type the chosen combination Heritrix login screen (The login may 
have to be &#39;admin&#39; IIRC).  That should grant you access.

Currently MANIFEST.MF for heritrix.jar looks like this:

